flowchart TD
    A([Start]) --> B["Initialize Game<br/>target word + forbidden list<br/>turn = 0"]
    B --> C["Hinter Agent<br/>Generate hint without<br/>forbidden words"]
    C --> D["Send hint to<br/>message queue"]
    D --> E["Guesser Agent<br/>Read hint + prior guesses<br/>Produce guess"]
    E --> F{Correct guess?}
    F -->|Yes| G["Game Won<br/>Announce target word"]
    F -->|No| H["Log wrong guess<br/>turn += 1"]
    H --> I{Turn limit<br/>reached?}
    I -->|Yes| J["Game Over<br/>Target unrevealed"]
    I -->|No| K["Update Guesser<br/>with wrong guess history"]
    K --> C
    G --> L([End])
    J --> L